text: hi my name is NAMESLOTA how may I help you
"Hello, NAMESLOTA."
What are you calling me about?
I was checking to make you sure your recent amazon purchase went well
"No, the order has not gone well."
What I ordered never arrived.
there seems to have been a problem with your payment
What would that be?
It didn't go through
Why is that?
the company didn't approve the payment
Who is the company?
Amazon?
no your credit card company.
It appears your billing info wasn't correct
"Oh, thanks for letting me know."
I guess I will contact them.
i can update it for you right now
I would rather go through my credit card company.
it looks like we just need a correct expiration date
What does that have to do with my billing info?
what you entered for the order is wrong and we can't ship your item without it
You said it was the billing info?
Wouldn't that be my address and not my card?
"billing info includes your address, expiration date and credit card number"
Can you remind me again what I ordered NAMESLOTA?
It has been awhile....
You should remember if your waiting for it
But you are looking at all my info right now.
So tell me.
